servinfo.title: Power Window Sub Switch Inspection

s1.ptxt: Remove front and/or rear door trim from door panel, refer to Step 1) to 3) of Front Door Glass Removal and Installation and/or Rear Door Glass Removal and Installation .
Remove power window sub switch from door trim.
Check for continuity between terminals at each switch condition.

servinfo.ptxt: If check result is not as specified, replace switch.
